msgstr "Quarkus 安全测试"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-overview.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For guidance on testing Quarkus Security features and ensuring that your Quarkus applications are securely protected, see the xref:security-testing.adoc[Security testing] guide."
msgstr "有关测试 Quarkus 安全功能以及确保您的 Quarkus 应用程序得到安全保护的指导，请参阅《 xref:security-testing.adoc[安全测试指南] 》。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/security-overview.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
